eta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Feiwellhub Naturals\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_KE\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Feiwellhub Naturals\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Premium food supplements and herbal wellness products.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon.png?2b67a4683078cab6\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"500x500\"/><link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&amp;family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white transition-all duration-200\n      border-b border-gray-100\"><div class=\"bg-sage text-white text-center text-xs py-2 px-4 font-body font-medium tracking-wide\">🌿 Free delivery on orders above Ksh 2,000  ·  Consult our wellness team before use  ·  Same-day Nairobi delivery</div><div class=\"w-[min(1280px,100%-2rem)] mx-auto flex items-center justify-between h-16 gap-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 shrink-0\" aria-label=\"Feiwellhub Naturals home\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Feiwellhub Naturals\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"60\" height=\"50\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ffeiwell-logo.94ea443d.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ffeiwell-logo.94ea443d.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ffeiwell-logo.94ea443d.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"leading-none\"><span class=\"font-display text-[1.3rem] font-semibold text-bark block tracking-tight\">Feiwellhub</span><span class=\"text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sage font-body\">Naturals</span></div></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-0.5 flex-1 justify-center\"><div class=\"relative\"><a class=\"px-3.5 py-2 text-[0.875rem] font-medium rounded-lg\n                    transition-all duration-150 block\n                    text-text-main hover:text-sage hover:bg-sage-pale\" href=\"/products\">All Products</a></div><div class=\"relative\"><button class=\"flex items-center gap-1 px-3.5 py-2 text-[0.875rem] font-medium\n                    rounded-lg transition-all duration-150\n                    text-text-main hover:text-sage hover:bg-sage-pale\" aria-expanded=\"false\">By Condition<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\n                    text-text-muted\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"relative\"><button class=\"flex items-center gap-1 px-3.5 py-2 text-[0.875rem] font-medium\n                    rounded-lg transition-all duration-150\n                    text-text-main hover:text-sage hover:bg-sage-pale\" aria-expanded=\"false\">By Supplement<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\n                    text-text-muted\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"relative\"><a class=\"px-3.5 py-2 text-[0.875rem] font-medium rounded-lg\n                    transition-all duration-150 block\n                    text-text-main hover:text-sage hover:bg-sage-pale\" href=\"/products?category=immune-support\">Immune Support</a></div><div class=\"relative\"><a class=\"px-3.5 py-2 text-[0.875rem] font-medium rounded-lg\n                    transition-all duration-150 block\n                    text-text-main hover:text-sage hover:bg-sage-pale\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a></div><div class=\"relative\"><a class=\"px-3.5 py-2 text-[0.875rem] font-medium rounded-lg\n                    transition-all duration-150 block\n                    text-text-main hover:text-sage hover:bg-sage-pale\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 shrink-0\"><a class=\"hidden lg:inline-flex btn btn-primary btn-sm text-xs px-5\" href=\"/contact\">Get Advice</a><button class=\"lg:hidden p-2 rounded-lg text-bark hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></header><main><section class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-100 py-14\"><div class=\"w-[min(1280px,100%-2rem)] mx-auto\"><span class=\"section-label block mb-2\">Legal</span><h1 class=\"text-bark\">Terms of Service</h1><p class=\"text-text-muted text-sm mt-2\">Last updated: January 2025</p></div></section><section class=\"py-14\"><div class=\"w-[min(1280px,100%-2rem)] mx-auto max-w-[800px]\"><div class=\"bg-cream border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl p-6 flex gap-4 mb-10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text text-sage shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><path d=\"M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\">By using our website or placing an order with <!-- -->Feiwellhub Naturals<!-- -->, you agree to these terms. Please read them carefully. If you have questions,<!-- --> <a class=\"text-sage hover:underline\" href=\"/contact\">contact us</a> <!-- -->before purchasing.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-8\"><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">1</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">About These Terms</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><p>These Terms of Service govern your use of the <!-- -->Feiwellhub Naturals<!-- --> website and your purchase of products from us. <!-- -->Feiwellhub Naturals<!-- --> is a natural wellness business registered and operating in Nairobi, Kenya.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">2</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">Products &amp; Health Disclaimer</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><p class=\"mb-3\">Our products are food supplements and natural wellness products. They are <strong class=\"text-bark font-semibold\">not medicines</strong> and are not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease.</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 flex flex-col gap-1.5 text-sm\"><li>Consult a qualified healthcare professional before starting any supplement</li><li>Results vary — we make no guarantees of specific outcomes</li><li>If pregnant, breastfeeding or on medication, consult your doctor first</li><li>Keep all products out of reach of children</li><li>Discontinue use if you experience any adverse reaction</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">3</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">Placing an Order</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><p>Orders are placed via WhatsApp or our contact form. An order is confirmed only when you receive written confirmation from us and payment has been received. We reserve the right to decline any order.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">4</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">Pricing &amp; Payment</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 flex flex-col gap-1.5 text-sm\"><li>All prices are in Kenyan Shillings (Ksh)</li><li>Prices may change without notice — the price at time of order confirmation applies</li><li>Payment is due before dispatch for new customers</li><li>Accepted methods: M-Pesa, bank transfer, cash on delivery (Nairobi only)</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">5</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">Delivery</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><p>Please refer to our <a class=\"text-sage hover:underline\" href=\"/shipping-policy\">Shipping Policy</a> for full delivery terms, areas and timelines.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">6</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">Returns &amp; Refunds</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><p>Please refer to our <a class=\"text-sage hover:underline\" href=\"/return-policy\">Return &amp; Refund Policy</a> for full terms.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">7</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">Intellectual Property</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><p>All content on this website — including text, images, logos and product descriptions — is the property of <!-- -->Feiwellhub Naturals<!-- -->. You may not reproduce or distribute our content without prior written permission.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">8</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">Limitation of Liability</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><p>To the maximum extent permitted by Kenyan law, <!-- -->Feiwellhub Naturals<!-- --> shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental or consequential damages arising from the use of our products or website. Our liability is limited to the value of the order in question.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">9</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">Website Use</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 flex flex-col gap-1.5 text-sm\"><li>You must be at least 18 years old to purchase from us</li><li>You agree not to misuse this website or attempt to gain unauthorised access</li><li>We reserve the right to restrict access to anyone who violates these terms</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">10</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">Governing Law</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><p>These terms are governed by the laws of Kenya. Any disputes shall be resolved under Kenyan jurisdiction.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">11</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">Changes to These Terms</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><p>We may update these terms at any time. The date at the top of this page shows the last update. Continued use of our website after changes constitutes acceptance.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-sage-pale rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-sm font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5\">12</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl text-bark mb-3\">Contact</h2><div class=\"text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed\"><p>Questions about these terms? Email us at<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:sales@feiwellhub.co.ke\" class=\"text-sage hover:underline\">sales@feiwellhub.co.ke</a> <!-- -->or <a class=\"text-sage hover:underline\" href=\"/contact\">send a message</a>.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-bark text-cream\"><div class=\"w-[min(1280px,100%-2rem)] mx-auto pt-16 pb-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-[1.8fr_1fr_1fr_1fr_1.4fr] gap-10 pb-10 border-b border-cream/10\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"Feiwellhub Naturals\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"82\" height=\"72\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\" object-contain brightness-0 invert sepia-[30%] saturate-[400%] hue-rotate-[10deg]\"